
ESP32-CAM local configuration
=============================

Copy `secrets.example.h` to `secrets.h` and replace the placeholder Wi-Fi values:

```
#define WIFI_SSID "your-wifi-ssid"
#define WIFI_PASSWORD "your-wifi-password"
#define CAMERA_HOSTNAME "chicken-barn-esp32cam"
```

`secrets.h` is ignored by Git so Wi-Fi credentials are not committed to the public repo.
The firmware can also be configured with PlatformIO `build_flags` that define the same
macros if you prefer not to create a local header.
